responses.text: This place appears like a vision in the mist.
The fog of war is no match for the mist of fate.
Look upon the Lord of Avernus and beware.
Easy now, this stuff is explosive!
I bring an end to magic.
The Self seeks to end the great schism.
Matter has been split from its intended form. These must be made to unite.
Nightmares, follow me into the light.
If you don't ride into battle, you don't ride at all.
Gonna ride this bat outta Hell like a bat outta Hell!
The dogs of war feast tonight!
There's a price on all their heads.
No job is too big, no fee is too big.
My blades will do the talking.
You can run but you can't hide.
What kind of pub is this?
Were you wanting to see some identification?
I fight any thing in the house.
Time to mash some faces, I'd say.
Oh, you want some of this… eh?
Oh, I'm a right proper basher.
You're not afraid of spiders, are you?
I fear neither beast nor blade.
I will stomp them to dust.
All that is light shall be cast in darkness.
Where goes my eye, goes my arrow.
A light to guide my way. A light to burn my foes.
I've a mind like a steel trap, and the physique to go with it!
I'm more than a bit tightly wound.
It's all fun and games until someone's frozen solid.
Is it cold in here or is it just me?
From the land behind the wall, I come.
I see where this road ends.
A mind sharper than any blade.
u Whaddya say Jex, you ready to play?
u Whaddaya waiting for? We have some gold to steal.
u Let's get into some mischief, shall we?
Darkness fears the break of dawn!
Where my shadow falls, there falls my foe.
My shadow shall darken all creation.
What I've seen goes far beyond death.
Who dares recall me from the grave?
The doors of death open wide.
I see a dark future for us all!
The days of fair weather are over.
The war storm is upon us.
By stormcraft, I shall lay my enemies low.
See you in the Seven Hells.
Time to paint the battlefield red.
My quiver and bow are ready!
The terrestrial sphere imbues my spirit.
My spirit accretes from a higher plane.
That which is arises from that which is not.
Time to shake things up and see where they settle.
The earth moves under my feet!
It is only right that I am cast into this world, for I had a hand in breaking it.
I was the hammer at the Founding.
On this alone of seven planes the final war is fought.
What long ago I shattered must be rendered whole.
New strength to shoulder the burden of a broken world.
Shady lanes and sunny glades await!
What an enchanting day for battle!
This fawn's afternoon is looking up!
I take form, consumer of worlds.
From void and shadow, I assemble.
From a place beyond time, and time beyond counting.
I have seen the end of time.
I'll paint this world as I see fit.
The battlefield is merely a canvas, waiting for my brush.
The strokes of my brush mark your fate.
Let's not get squirrely now, it'd be a shame to have to kill you.
You ever hear the one about the tortoise and the hare and the squirrel that shot 'em both?
The wood teaches one rule: step fast or you're snack meat.
Who said you could stroll in my woods?
Ah, the potential for sacrifice is great!
There can never be too much sacrifice.
So begins a new age of knowledge.
The Light guides me on my quest.
It's a new age of magic!
An old vessel, but more than seaworthy.
Step lively now, your Admiral is on board!
Whatever they brought, it won't be enough.
I've come to put an end to hope.
The elements of my nature are in torment.
By the impure powers of nature.
I am the dead of winter!
From the frozen pool, I rise.
From cold death, I rise again.
I've got fire in my eyes!
Hell hath no fury like me.
All hells broken loose, and I hold the pieces.
Nature is not for the weak.
They will find my blade sharp, and cruel.
Who keeps the company of wolves?
My horn is sharp, my pike is sharper still.
Keep your eye on my horn!
Under my hoof you will find your fate.
Spreading enlightenment at the tip of my spear.
To war! And glorious conquest! Yaaahh!
To those behind, rally! To those ahead... Kneel!
There is no heart colder than mine.
None can stand against Sun Wukong.
I've outwitted gods. Smashing a glowing rock should be no problem.
Don't look so surprised, human. My arrival was foretold.
Your existence is proof that justice is only a myth.
A true reaper is never so petty as you.
It's all I can do to keep my pistols at my side...
Is this why my daughter died? So I could help you eons later in a meaningless fight?
Are you sure this world deserves your help?
An amusing fool, but a fool nonetheless.
I sing the Siren song of war.
I summon the forces of nature.
Ah, the sun in my leaves.
I'm the beast of bedtime tales.
My purpose is clear, my targets doomed.
I like this part! Me too.
Pleased to meet ya. Likewise I'm sure.
Hittin stuff is fun. Hah aha ha ha ha!
My hammer is ready in the service of the All-knowing One.
Where piety fails, my hammer falls.
The All-knowing One protects us all.
Fear not my friends, our guardian is here.
Like those odds, do you, hmm?
From the outer dark I come.
From the fortress afloat in the dark.
My wings beat with the rhythms of eternity.
Their sanity I'll shatter, their dreams of conquest I'll destroy.
The honorable Donté Panlin, at your service.
Please, please. Hold your applause until the end.
I have never run from a fight. But sometimes I do roll.
I'm here to blur the line between life and death.
Where falls my shadow, fells my blade.
Don't blink, or you'll miss me.
In the blink of an eye.
Death at my hands is an honor.
We are coiled, ready to strike.
What is this, a game of some sort?
A likely way to pass a fraction of an eon.
This should be less tiresome than another age in chrysalis.
Oh, I love a good slaughter.
I channel the power of the Nether Reaches.
Who needs a blade when you have oblivion?
A new age of dark magic starts now.
There will be pain, there will be screaming.
So begins the reign of pain.
Your ashes will fall like rain.
To the Narrow Maze with you!
I speak softly, but carry a sharp knife.
Heh-ho, you didn't see that coming.
My thirst for knowledge cannot be quenched.
I shall see what they have in store.
No sorcery lies beyond my grasp.
I am no thief. I merely borrow.
There are none who cannot be mimicked.
This time it is the demon who will do the summoning!
I will scatter all who gather here today.
I sense the proximity of souls…
Hear me, I speak for the shades!
For our fathers, gone beyond the hills!
A hush falls on the battlefield.
The deep ones send me forth.
If I'd known I'd end up here, I'd have stayed in Dark Reef Prison.
Oh no, you'll bait no hook with me.
Perfect. I've got baking to do!
I love the smell of black powder in the morning.
You looking for cookin tips, violence, or both?
Take your best shot. I will.
I come: Lock, stock and barrel.
I call the shots around here.
My aim is truer than ever!
From another dimension, a world beyond.
I have come here a stranger, lost.
My iron will shall break them.
I'll break their spirits and their backs.
Feel the wind in your hair!
Everyone complains about the weather…well, I'm doing something about it!
Told you a storm was coming!
How much powder'd you pack into that one? Uh, most of it!
If you want explosions. Accept no substitutes!
Measurements made. Bombs built. Powder's dry. Okay, let's blow something up!
My blades and my mind are as one.
The self-righteous shall choke on their sanctimony.
From the Hell of Hells I come.
Link A demon's rage is stronger than death.
I cut things. It's what I do. What else would I do?
Trees? What do you mean there's trees out there?
They can try to stop me. They can try!
I am perfectly suited for this environment.
Sometimes I think you only want me for my hazard suit!
I have several theories I'd like to put into practice.
Who breathes life into these old stones?
Sticks and stones will break their bones!
Trees can be ferocious if provoked.
The strong shall eat the weak.
My hate shall burn you down.
Well well! It's been a while since I came this far south.
Who's ready for a fight? The first hit is free! Anyone?
A lord's work is never done.
I bring the song of death.
Come not near the darkwoods where my kindred sleep.
It is my spirit that keeps me safe, and not mere armor.
I'll have you in my claws!
Power like a promise of revenge!
My enemies will taste my venom.
That which passes beyond the veil must forever stay.
No soul may elude my gaze.
I am the unyielding face of death.
None may flee death for long.
Existence as you perceive it is but a shade of the infinite realm.
The great confluence approaches and my time finally comes.
This path leads amongst my brothers, where they have long wished I'd go.
A new chapter in my Black Grimoire.
The loom weaves and a new pattern appears.
More fates for me to weave.
My next arrow will find its mark.
Some breathe fire. I breathe ice.
I carry winter wherever I go!
I bring the breath of winter to the field of war.
With bones and spells I come.
I descend to walk among mortals.
